title: Toast Cafe and Sandwich Bar
typeOfFood: Vegan-friendly, Western, Fast food, Salad bar, Take-out, Bakery, Non-veg
description: Serves meat, veg options available. Small cafe open for breakfast/lunch with wide range of vegan pies (lentil, curry, potato, shepherds and more). Also has vegan treats (raw balls), soy/coconut/almond milk for coffee, vegan smoothies/shakes, salads, veggie burger, veggie sandwiches. Almost direct access to the Adelaide train station.
